pyftk
=====

python binding for ftk (http://code.google.com/p/ftk/).

features
========

* use python ctypes, not c
* provides c-style interface, not oo-style

dependencies
============

python2.6
ftk 0.6

install
=======

$ git clone git://github.com/htbegin/pyftk.git
$ cd pyftk
$ git checkout pyftk
$ cd script_binding/python
$ sudo python setup.py install

test
====

$ git clone git://github.com/htbegin/pyftk.git
$ cd pyftk
$ git checkout pyftk
$ cd script_binding/python
$ ./runner.py test/

demo
====

$ git clone git://github.com/htbegin/pyftk.git
$ cd pyftk
$ git checkout pyftk
$ cd script_binding/python
$ ./runner.py demo/
